- **JSON SSOT**: Implemented [resolve_parameter](file:///home/kizabgd/Desktop/Istrazivanje/scripts/config_manager.py#19-37) in [trinity.py](file:///home/kizabgd/Desktop/Istrazivanje/scripts/trinity.py) to prioritize [trinity_config.json](file:///home/kizabgd/Desktop/Istrazivanje/trinity_config.json).
